01:40:06,720 --> 01:40:13,360
how does the value of the color of the quark change as I travel along some path, okay?

1464
01:40:13,360 --> 01:40:19,720
I can connect these two points in space with some path, and I can ask how the axes that

1465
01:40:19,720 --> 01:40:24,080
